      <title>蘋果執行長庫克抵達越南會見用戶，加強供應商關係</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-ceo-tim-cook-arrives-vietnam-meet-users-boost-supplier-ties-2024-04-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根據官方媒體報道，蘋果執行長庫克週一抵達河內，開始對越南進行為期兩天的訪問，越南是這家iPhone 製造商的重要製造中心，預計他在此期間會見學生和內容創作者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-ceo-tim-cook-arrives-vietnam-meet-users-boost-supplier-ties-2024-04-15/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 04:07:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
